title: Chris Lake - Essential Mix - 14-08-2010
description:
Chris Lake is one of the UK's most accomplished house producers. He hit the top 40 in 2006 with 'Changes' and scored the first 'Essential New Tune' of 2010 on Pete Tong's show with the Michael Woods remix of 'I Said'. He is a resident at Cream in Ibiza for the Deadmau5 & Friends night.
